              "displayName": "Thomas Graves",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Chicago"
            },
            "body": "Can you please clarify but what you mean by performance, what is actually be affected, and in general more details about how you are running these tests?   Are you perhaps referring to the fact that if you set memory-mb high, it allows a lot of MR jobs on a single node at once and overload the cpu?  If so then you should be using cpu scheduling. ",
