              "active": false,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "yarn.nodemanager.resource.memory-mb should ideally be fixed per node in a YARN cluster. As [~tgaves] said, we should look at how the individual tasks are scheduled (spread out) and other relevant information. ",
