            },
            "body": "[~nravi], what scheduler are you using? If you use CapacityScheduler, YARN-893 can be related issue. ",
            "updateAuthor": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=ozawa",
              "name": "ozawa",
              "key": "ozawa",
              "avatarUrls": {
