              "displayName": "Vinod Kumar Vavilapalli",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "Asia/Kolkata"
            },
            "body": "Tx for all the updates, [~nravi], but can you please make clear the issues that you think are needed to be fixed?",
            "updateAuthor": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=vinodkv",
              "name": "vinodkv",
              "key": "vinodkv",
              "avatarUrls": {
                "48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452",
                "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452",
                "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452",
                "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"
              },
              "displayName": "Vinod Kumar Vavilapalli",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "Asia/Kolkata"
            },
            "created": "2014-05-29T02:27:26.113+0000",
            "updated": "2014-05-29T02:27:26.113+0000"
          },
          {
            "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12713424/comment/14012134",
            "id": "14012134",
            "author": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=nravi",
              "name": "nravi",
              "key": "nravi",
              "avatarUrls": {
                "48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452",
                "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452",
                "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452",
                "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"
              },
              "displayName": "Nishkam Ravi",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "Etc/UTC"
            },
            "body": "Sure. There seem to be multiple issues. Two seem to clearly stand out:\n\n1. Performance degrades with FIFO for large values of memory-mb in both single-job and multi-job mode. Observed for multiple benchmarks including TeraSort, TeraValidate, TeraGen, WordCount, ShuffleText. Issue: FIFO seems to be allocating too many jobs at once on a single node.\n2. Performance with Capacity scheduler suffers for large values of memory-mb only for TeraValidate (in single-job mode). Issue: why does Capacity scheduler regress for TeraValidate? ",
            "updateAuthor": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=nravi",
              "name": "nravi",
              "key": "nravi",
              "avatarUrls": {
                "48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452",
                "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452",
                "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452",
                "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"
              },
              "displayName": "Nishkam Ravi",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "Etc/UTC"
            },
            "created": "2014-05-29T06:56:58.836+0000",
            "updated": "2014-05-29T06:56:58.836+0000"
